                            **************************************
                            *                                    *
                            *    Where in the World is ...       *
                            *                                    *
                            **************************************

Application to show off Geolocation features in HTML5 and Javascript.  Built with the Ruby on Rails framework.

Live on Heroku at http://witwib.heroku.com

Feel free to add your location.  Accept permissions to allow WitWiB to find your location.  Copy/Past the
Latitude and Longitude.  Then add a note about your location.  Please include:

    * Address
    * Business Name
    * Your Email
    * Your Name

